    "John Trapp": "Abner made himself strong. ] See #2Sa 2:8,9 .\nVer.\n6. Abner made himself strong.] See #2Sa 2:8,",
    "930072315325": "And it came to pass, while there was war between the house of\nSaul and the house of David `[char_David_Rut_4]`, etc.] As long as that continued, as it did until\nthe following quarrel happened between Ishbosheth and Abner:\nthat Abner made himself strong for the house of Saul; or was strongly in\nthe interest of that house, and used his utmost endeavours to support and\nconfirm it.\nVer."
